title: Rapport: Över 10 000 ryssar har dött i Ukraina
cleaned_sentences: The identity of more than 10,000 Russians has been confirmed by BBC Russia through open sources.
Several of them come from Russia's poor parts and have probably been part of the military for a long time, believes military expert Joakim Paasikivi.
